Unless you are using a pre 74 DP, all the DP heads were thickened up and all
the replacement SP heads were beefed up too. If you buy a new VW head,
either
flavor, you will only get the thick heads. Most of the aftermarket heads are
also thicker.

67 Single Cab, DP 1641cc 34 PICT-3
71 Trike 1776cc Dual T-4 34 PDSIT-3
VolksAir 1585cc 31 PICT
http://mywebpage.netscape.com/alphahr/case.html
Ray, Kent WA
